00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.801
Best Breed Ever! Chihuahuas
Chihuahuas' ancestors existed as long ago

00:00:01.801 --> 00:00:03.430
as 9th century AD!
The smaller, modern breed originated in Mexico's

00:00:03.430 --> 00:00:03.570
state of Chihuahua and were foot warmers for
the nobility

00:00:03.570 --> 00:00:03.691
Chihuahuas are the smallest dog breed in the
world!

00:00:03.691 --> 00:00:03.830
Most are 6-9 inches tall and weigh under 6
lbs

00:00:03.830 --> 00:00:07.641
Chihuahuas love to cuddle and they love to
burrow into pillows and blankets

00:00:07.641 --> 00:00:14.641
They tremble when anxious or cold, so sweaters
and booties are recommended

00:00:27.081 --> 00:00:34.081
Chihuahuas have big brains for their size
and are highly trainable if you start early!

